<p><a name="Textbooks" id="Textbooks"></a></p>
<h3><span class="editsection">[<a href="/w/index.php?title=Functional_magnetic_resonance_imaging&amp;action=edit&amp;section=21" title="Edit section: Textbooks">edit</a>]</span> <span class="mw-headline">Textbooks</span></h3>
<p>Scott A. Huettel, Allen W. Song, Gregory McCarthy, <i>Functional Magnetic Resonance Imaging</i>, Sinauer Associates, 2004, <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0878932887" class="internal">ISBN 0-87893-288-7</a></p>
